D21

leaflet(width = "100%", height = 800) %>%
  addTiles() %>%
  addPolygons(data = map_21,
              color = "black", weight = 2, smoothFactor = 0.5, opacity = 1.0, fillOpacity = 0.2,
              group = "District") %>%
  addPolygons(data = map_block_group_filter,
              color = "blue", weight = 1, smoothFactor = 0.5, opacity = 1.0, fillOpacity = 0.35,
              group = "Block Group",
              highlight = highlightOptions(
                weight = 5,
                fillOpacity = 0.7,
                bringToFront = TRUE)) %>%
  addPolygons(data = map_block_filter,
              color = "red", weight = 1, smoothFactor = 0.5, opacity = 1.0, fillOpacity = 0.7,
              fillColor = ~pal(population),
              group = "Block") %>%
  addPolygons(data = map_neighborhoods_filter,
              color = "green", weight = 2, smoothFactor = 0.5, opacity = 1.0, fillOpacity = 0.35,
              label = map_neighborhoods_filter$NH_NAME,
              group = "Neighborhood") %>%
  addLayersControl(overlayGroups = c("District", "Block Group", "Block", "Neighborhood")) %>%
  addLegend(pal = pal, values = c(0, 1000), opacity = 0.7, title = "Population", position = "bottomright")
